oF of $K\\gamma+\\alpha$ for networks with uniform user\ndistribution, $\\alpha > \\hat{\\eta}$, and non-integer\n$\\frac{\\alpha}{\\hat{\\eta}}$, without imposing any other constraints. Finally,\nwe use numerical simulations to assess how non-uniform user distribution\nimpacts the DoF performance and illustrate that the proposed scheme provides a\nnoticeable improvement over unicasting for uneven distributions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 23 Apr 2023 11:40:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-25"}
